OL,3,CMan threatened to 'stab and slice'
OL,4,Ccollege students in YouTube video
OL,6,FA 21-year-old who posted a threatening
OL,7,Fvideo online, in which he claimed he
OL,8,Fwas going to "cut, stab and slice"
OL,9,Fpeople at his former college, has been
OL,10,Fsentenced.
OL,12,FOliver Beynon posted the video on
OL,13,FYouTube in August 2025, which was then
OL,14,Fseen by members of Merthyr Tydfil
OL,15,FCollege who were "upset and panicked"
OL,16,Fby what they saw.
