OL,3,CMan threatened to 'stab and slice'
OL,4,Ccollege students in YouTube video
OL,6,FIn the video, Beynon is wearing a
OL,7,Ffedora hat and face mask and threatens
OL,8,Fto kill students at the college. The
OL,9,F21-year-old describes himself as "the
OL,10,FWelshman" and can be seen staring
OL,11,Fintensely at the camera.
OL,13,FHe can then be heard saying: "Next
OL,14,FSeptember, not this week but next
OL,15,Fweek, I'm going to kill (everyone) in
OL,16,FMerthyr Tydfil College in south Wales.
OL,17,FI am going to stab, cut, slice and
OL,18,Fopen their insides out."
