OL,3,CMan threatened to 'stab and slice'
OL,4,Ccollege students in YouTube video
OL,6,FHe goes into more graphic details
OL,7,Fabout the violence he is threatening
OL,8,Fand also talks about "taking over a
OL,9,Fbody" before adding: "The god I'm here
OL,10,Fand I'm going to kill every person in
OL,11,FMerthyr Tydfil College."
OL,13,FThe video was quickly reported to the
OL,14,Fpolice, who were able to identify
OL,15,FBeynon from the footage. His father
OL,16,Fhad also contacted 101 after being
OL,17,Fmade aware of the video.
