OL,6,FPolice attended the defendant's home
OL,7,Fin Fochriw, Caerphilly, and seized a
OL,8,Fnumber of devices - one was found to
OL,9,Fcontain the offending video.
OL,11,FDuring his interview, Beynon admitted
OL,12,Fhe had posted the video and said he
OL,13,Fhad been suffering with mental health
OL,14,Fproblems.
OL,16,FHe said the video "escalated quickly"
OL,17,Fand he regretted making it, adding
OL,18,Fthat he heard voices in his head
OL,19,Ftelling him to make the video.
