OL,4,Ccollege students in YouTube video
OL,6,FHe also told officers he was "under so
OL,7,Fmuch pressure", was being bullied and
OL,8,Fhad received death threats.
OL,10,FProsecutor Byron Broadstock said the
OL,11,Fdefendant suffers from dyslexia and
OL,12,Fautism and spends much of his time in
OL,13,Fhis bedroom watching YouTube and
OL,14,Fplaying video games.
OL,16,FThe prosecutor said the video had a
OL,17,F"profound impact" on Merthyr Tydfil
OL,18,FCollege and its students, who were
OL,19,Fleft "upset and panicked".
