OL,6,FBeynon later pleaded guilty to sending
OL,7,Fa threatening communication. The court
OL,8,Fheard he has no previous convictions.
OL,10,FIn mitigation, Alice Sykes said her
OL,11,Fclient was of a young age and lacked
OL,12,Fmaturity but he had co-operated with
OL,13,Fthe investigation and made full
OL,14,Fadmissions.
OL,16,FOn 11 February at Cardiff Crown Court,
OL,17,FRecorder Christian Jowett sentenced
OL,18,FBeynon to six months imprisonment,
OL,19,Fsuspended for 18 months.
